    Ashikhmin-Premoze GSF is designed for use with Isotropic NDF;0;0\nNode;AmplifyShaderEditor.StickyNoteNode,
    AmplifyShaderEditor, Version=0.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=null;5930;-8816,768;Inherit;False;201.5207;111.8501;;;0,0,0,1;Designed
