    AmplifyShaderEditor, Version=0.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=null;6463;-9728,12464;Inherit;False;375.5869;136.5718;;;0,0,0,1;In
    the Unity SG Geometry term and Normal Distribution term functions they need roughness
