    Version=0.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=null;6466;-8992,10912;Inherit;False;383.988;159.9665;;;0,0,0,1;Anisotropic
    NDF functions produce the normal distribution Anisotropically. $$This allows
